1
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:29,960
Father.

2
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:33,700
Haven't I told you before?

3
00:00:34,030 --> 00:00:35,830
Whether in public or in private,

4
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:37,700
you should just call me "Master."

5
00:00:37,880 --> 00:00:40,140
"Our bodies are gifts from our parents."

6
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:41,560
This life of mine is

7
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:43,420
entirely a gift from you, Father.

8
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:45,150
Had you not taken me in

9
00:00:45,390 --> 00:00:46,960
as your student in Jiankang

10
00:00:46,960 --> 00:00:48,320
and guided me so diligently,

11
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:50,240
I would never have
reached where I am today.

12
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:51,350
Everything I believe in and aspire to

13
00:00:51,350 --> 00:00:53,280
has also been nurtured by your teaching.

14
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:56,010
I would never dare
show you anything but respect.

15
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,600
Good.

16
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:03,280
My good son.

17
00:01:10,950 --> 00:01:13,150
You are every bit a son of the Xie family.

18
00:01:14,710 --> 00:01:16,840
You've done well these past few years.

19
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:19,150
You used the reform as a pretext
to reshape the salt and iron monopoly

20
00:01:19,150 --> 00:01:20,310
and clear the waterways.

21
00:01:20,310 --> 00:01:21,870
The people will remember you

22
00:01:21,870 --> 00:01:22,800
and support you.

23
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:26,950
But the reform

24
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:30,039
was ultimately initiated by Xiao Wuyi.

25
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,039
If you want to become

26
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:37,590
the true ruler of the realm,

27
00:01:38,039 --> 00:01:40,920
you must sweep aside

28
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,780
anyone who stands in your way,

29
00:01:45,479 --> 00:01:46,840
one by one, like dust.

30
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:24,280
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

31
00:03:24,380 --> 00:03:27,240
[Episode 22]

32
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,190
Xiao Wuyi,

33
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:34,370
you need to learn to take what you want.

34
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:48,640
♪ One glance from near stirs my heart ♪

35
00:03:48,860 --> 00:03:51,410
♪ This fleeting moment ♪

36
00:03:53,110 --> 00:03:57,120
♪ Tugs the threads woven by fate ♪

37
00:03:54,310 --> 00:03:55,240
Xiao Wuyi.

38
00:03:57,290 --> 00:03:59,290
♪ Bound tight evermore ♪

39
00:03:58,870 --> 00:03:59,960
Do you hear me?

40
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,120
I hear you.

41
00:04:08,590 --> 00:04:09,280
Good.

42
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,120
You're really drunk.

43
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,510
I'm not.

44
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,660
I still have a New Year's gift for you.

45
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,720
What do you think?

46
00:04:44,110 --> 00:04:48,450
♪ You know my resolve
to live and die together ♪

47
00:04:48,470 --> 00:04:52,130
♪ Believe in my persistence that
I won't run away ♪

48
00:04:52,150 --> 00:04:56,300
♪ You know I'm unyielding ♪

49
00:04:57,120 --> 00:05:00,040
♪ Don't give up or dodge ♪

50
00:04:58,290 --> 00:04:59,050
My red steed.

51
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:04,410
♪ You know me, seeing things
through from start to finish ♪

52
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:05,240
My Miraculous Craft
has made a lot of money,

53
00:05:04,930 --> 00:05:09,050
♪ You see my move
under rebellious cover ♪

54
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,560
so I redeemed it.

55
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,110
You're going to the battlefield,

56
00:05:08,110 --> 00:05:09,310
so you need the finest horse.

57
00:05:09,310 --> 00:05:13,300
♪ You know me, I'm willing to be
with you till the end ♪

58
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:12,270
It can bring you home.

59
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:17,250
♪ Burn the fire in my heart ♪

60
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:19,430
Yaoyao.

61
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:22,410
♪ Sincere hearts remain as of old ♪

62
00:05:25,140 --> 00:05:26,140
I'll do my best...

63
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,600
to spend every New Year with you.

64
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,360
Wait, not this one.

65
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:04,330
I have a Hetian white jade crown

66
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,850
that Yaoyao gave me.

67
00:06:06,870 --> 00:06:07,560
Today

68
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:10,130
is the day she'll be officially invested.

69
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,420
I want to wear that one.

70
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:12,180
Yes.

71
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:22,320
To Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

72
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,050
Grand Tutor Xie,

73
00:06:26,070 --> 00:06:27,070
have you heard?

74
00:06:27,090 --> 00:06:28,870
Something terrible happened
at the grain canal.

75
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:30,870
The Xiao family embezzled funds
for the canal.

76
00:06:30,870 --> 00:06:32,390
They replaced river sand
with mud and silt,

77
00:06:32,390 --> 00:06:33,720
causing the grain canal to collapse,

78
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,430
and nearly 100 laborers
were killed or injured.

79
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:37,630
The County Sheriff has hanged himself.

80
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:40,650
The outraged crowds
have already reached Jiankang.

81
00:06:41,430 --> 00:06:42,830
There are so many guests today.

82
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:43,510
Yes.

83
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:46,310
Congratulations, congratulations.

84
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:47,170
Please come in.

85
00:06:49,070 --> 00:06:49,920
Why have so many

86
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:52,240
officials' families come to attend
the ceremony today?

87
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:54,040
Congratulations, congratulations.

88
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,170
Did you invite them?

89
00:06:56,390 --> 00:06:57,480
Of course not.

90
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,720
It must've been Wuyi.

91
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,680
I didn't.

92
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:00,480
Then...

93
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:02,360
Father, don't worry about it.

94
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,800
It's not every day
Wuyi throws such a grand affair.

95
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,360
Of course they came to help him
make a good showing.

96
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:08,110
His Highness Prince Qi has arrived!

97
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:10,730
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

98
00:07:13,350 --> 00:07:14,410
Congratulations.

99
00:07:14,870 --> 00:07:15,870
I'm not late, am I?

100
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:19,330
Your Highness has arrived
at just the right time.

101
00:07:20,310 --> 00:07:20,950
Thank you.

102
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:33,680
From now on,

103
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,159
we are no longer brothers,

104
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:39,270
but ruler and subject.

105
00:07:45,810 --> 00:07:47,140
Who is beating the drum?

106
00:07:47,310 --> 00:07:49,040
This must be a grave injustice.

107
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:57,159
Someone is sounding the Petition Drum.

108
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:58,020
Petition Drum?

109
00:08:00,270 --> 00:08:01,070
It's struck only when the people

110
00:08:01,070 --> 00:08:01,920
have suffered a great injustice

111
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,240
or when enemy forces are invading.

112
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:05,300
Anyone who dares to strike that drum,

113
00:08:05,510 --> 00:08:07,040
whether their accusation is true or false,

114
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,720
must first endure 30 strikes of the cane

115
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:10,680
to prove they're not
making a false accusation.

116
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,430
Wouldn't that leave them dead or crippled?

117
00:08:12,430 --> 00:08:14,560
Therefore, unless someone has
genuinely suffered a serious injustice,

118
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:16,510
no one would risk their own life
like this.

119
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:19,190
Something major
is about to happen at court.

120
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:25,140
It has begun.

121
00:08:32,690 --> 00:08:33,380
My Lord!

122
00:08:34,390 --> 00:08:35,630
Who is it you intend to accuse?

123
00:08:35,630 --> 00:08:37,870
We accuse the Commander of the Beifu Army,

124
00:08:37,870 --> 00:08:40,240
the Heir of Prince Jing'an, Xiao Wuyi,

125
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:42,720
and his brother, Xiao Yao,
supervisor of the grain canal works.

126
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,320
What?

127
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:45,790
My Lord, please seek justice for us!

128
00:08:57,390 --> 00:08:59,250
The auspicious hour has arrived.

129
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:11,440
We respectfully invite Prince Qi,
the Regent, to bestow

130
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:14,550
the imperial decree and seal upon
the Consort of the Heir of Prince Jing'an

131
00:09:14,550 --> 00:09:17,150
and read out
the proclamation of investiture.

132
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,200
Report!

133
00:09:39,510 --> 00:09:42,040
Where are the accused,
Xiao Wuyi and Xiao Yao?

134
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,790
I pay my respects to Your Highness.

135
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:47,870
Your Highness,

136
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,320
I have no wish to disrupt

137
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:51,080
the Heir's Consort investiture ceremony.

138
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:53,210
But the Petition Drum has been struck.

139
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,670
According to the laws of Ye,

140
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:56,670
the main culprits
must be detained immediately:

141
00:09:56,670 --> 00:09:59,240
Young Lord Xiao
and Eldest Young Master Xiao.

142
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:02,240
Please forgive the offense.

143
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,040
How insolent!

144
00:10:04,870 --> 00:10:06,550
Today, at the investiture ceremony,

145
00:10:06,550 --> 00:10:08,870
I'd like to see who dares arrest them!

146
00:10:09,830 --> 00:10:11,480
The Ministry of Justice never

147
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:13,510
makes arrests without evidence.

148
00:10:13,870 --> 00:10:16,000
The grain canal in Hexi has collapsed,

149
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:18,440
causing over 1,000 casualties
and public outrage.

150
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,320
Our investigation found

151
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,960
that County Magistrate Wei Min,
a man of humble birth,

152
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:22,870
was personally promoted
by Young Lord Xiao.

153
00:10:22,870 --> 00:10:23,910
In his home,

154
00:10:23,910 --> 00:10:25,960
we found years of correspondence
between him

155
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,750
and Young Lord Xiao
and Eldest Young Master Xiao,

156
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:29,480
along with 1,000 taels of gold.

157
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:32,360
Moreover, the letters reveal evidence

158
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:34,360
that the Xiaos embezzled
the canal repair funds

159
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:36,320
and abused their power for personal gain.

160
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:38,920
Commandant of Justice,
if the sons are guilty,

161
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:41,550
shouldn't the father be guilty as well?

162
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:44,010
You may arrest the two of them,

163
00:10:44,340 --> 00:10:46,310
but you'll be taking me too!

164
00:10:47,150 --> 00:10:48,750
I'd like to see which of you dares!

165
00:10:48,750 --> 00:10:49,950
Take Prince Jing'an,

166
00:10:50,030 --> 00:10:52,160
the Heir, and Eldest Young Master Xiao

167
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:55,050
to the Court of Judicial Review together.

168
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,790
Yes, Your Highness.

169
00:10:57,550 --> 00:10:58,840
Order the Three Judicial Offices
to send officials

170
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:01,670
to conduct a thorough investigation
at the grain canal.

171
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:02,910
If they have been wronged,

172
00:11:02,910 --> 00:11:04,570
I will ensure justice is done.

173
00:11:06,550 --> 00:11:07,750
If they are guilty...

174
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:12,400
I will never allow anyone

175
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,870
to escape the law.

176
00:11:16,270 --> 00:11:18,800
Prince Jing'an,
please forgive the offense.

177
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:24,000
Young Lord Xiao, please.

178
00:11:29,350 --> 00:11:31,760
Don't worry. I'll be back.

179
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:56,280
Your Highness,
please bestow the decree and seal.

180
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:07,000
Your Highness, please proceed with
the investiture.

181
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:23,800
[Court of Judicial Review]

182
00:12:38,270 --> 00:12:40,240
Young Lord Xiao, you seem so composed.

183
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:41,370
Are you that certain

184
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:44,840
I won't find
conclusive evidence against you?

185
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,720
There is a list in my residence

186
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,600
recording every official

187
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,720
who has ever attempted

188
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:49,910
to bribe me.

189
00:12:50,630 --> 00:12:53,230
I've already sent a copy
to the Eastern Palace.

190
00:12:53,270 --> 00:12:56,000
Now I'll hand the original copy
of the list to you.

191
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,440
If such a list really exists,

192
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:58,750
why didn't you mention it earlier?

193
00:12:58,750 --> 00:13:00,210
Today, before the public,

194
00:13:00,510 --> 00:13:02,150
the Petition Drum has been struck,

195
00:13:02,150 --> 00:13:04,200
so you've come
bearing the will of the people.

196
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:05,510
Whether the accusations are true or false,

197
00:13:05,510 --> 00:13:08,240
they must go through the Court of Judicial Review's process
to convince everyone.

198
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:11,120
If I hadn't come,
it would've damaged your reputation.

199
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,030
And by coming,

200
00:13:12,910 --> 00:13:14,840
I placed my bet on your competence.

201
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:16,270
In that case,

202
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:18,670
I should be thanking you, Young Lord Xiao?

203
00:13:18,670 --> 00:13:19,930
There is one more thing

204
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,390
I'd ask you to consider,
Commandant of Justice.

205
00:13:21,390 --> 00:13:23,050
Please go on, Young Lord Xiao.

206
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:25,390
I've long heard
that you're strict and impartial.

207
00:13:25,390 --> 00:13:27,120
However, my father is elderly,

208
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:29,000
and my elder brother's leg
is badly crippled.

209
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:30,390
Neither could endure torture.

210
00:13:30,390 --> 00:13:31,910
Moreover, every order
regarding the grain canal work

211
00:13:31,910 --> 00:13:33,120
was issued by me.

212
00:13:33,510 --> 00:13:34,840
If torture is to be used,

213
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,630
I'm willing to endure it in their place.

214
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:38,720
Xiao Wuyi, don't shield me!

215
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,200
Since I dared to come in,

216
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,640
I am not afraid of interrogation!

217
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:43,300
What do you mean by "elderly"?

218
00:13:43,670 --> 00:13:45,750
I'm sturdier
than the two of them put together!

219
00:13:45,750 --> 00:13:47,280
Interrogate me if you must!

220
00:13:47,670 --> 00:13:48,910
Rest assured, everyone.

221
00:13:48,910 --> 00:13:50,790
If this turns out to be a frame-up,

222
00:13:50,980 --> 00:13:54,580
I will absolutely restore the good name of

223
00:13:54,750 --> 00:13:55,750
your household.

224
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:04,130
I entered prison

225
00:14:04,910 --> 00:14:06,120
precisely to see

226
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:08,000
just how far

227
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:10,670
the person behind all this
is willing to go.

228
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:20,630
Yuanji.

229
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:24,960
Mother had some calming tonic

230
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:25,960
and is asleep now.

231
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,440
The letters and ledgers in the household

232
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:30,640
have all been seized.

233
00:14:30,870 --> 00:14:31,960
Could it be that the Ministry of Justice

234
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:32,870
has been acting under someone's orders,

235
00:14:32,870 --> 00:14:33,930
trying to frame us?

236
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:36,410
I don't think so.

237
00:14:36,670 --> 00:14:38,080
Commandant of Justice Lu, who came today,

238
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:39,740
was newly promoted last year.

239
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:41,080
During these years of reform,

240
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,000
while serving in the provinces,

241
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,440
he punished commoners
who cheated in the marketplace

242
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:45,030
and sentenced noble clans
who seized land by force alike.

243
00:14:45,030 --> 00:14:46,080
He's a ruthless but upright official

244
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:48,000
who enforces the law without favor.

245
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,120
Since he personally came to
make the arrest today,

246
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:52,450
he surely wouldn't act without evidence.

247
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:53,750
The plaintiffs

248
00:14:53,750 --> 00:14:55,360
accuse the Beifu Army of embezzling

249
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,790
and taking bribes
during the canal repairs,

250
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:57,750
and cutting corners on the work—

251
00:14:57,750 --> 00:14:59,630
which caused the grain canal to collapse

252
00:14:59,630 --> 00:15:00,720
and killed many conscripted laborers.

253
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:02,050
Yao would never do that.

254
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:09,360
Letters, ledgers...

255
00:15:12,030 --> 00:15:12,630
Nanxing.

256
00:15:13,150 --> 00:15:13,630
My Lady.

257
00:15:13,790 --> 00:15:15,630
You have a photographic memory
for the accounts.

258
00:15:15,630 --> 00:15:18,890
You've been helping me
with the accounts these past years.

259
00:15:21,870 --> 00:15:23,550
So help me reconstruct them.

260
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:25,960
Yes.

261
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:30,360
Ledgers...

262
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:32,600
Letters...

263
00:15:34,550 --> 00:15:35,630
Handwriting...

264
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:42,340
What's wrong, Yuanji?

265
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:45,720
Nothing.

266
00:15:46,410 --> 00:15:47,810
I just suddenly realized

267
00:15:48,150 --> 00:15:50,550
I haven't seen
Qing Long and Yan Yue around.

268
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:52,840
Right, where are they?

269
00:15:56,550 --> 00:15:58,950
Xiao Wuyi and Xiao Ju
have been imprisoned.

270
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:01,670
Have you prepared

271
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:04,070
the forged correspondence I asked for?

272
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:11,760
Afraid it'll be exposed?

273
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:15,210
For the Xiao family,

274
00:16:16,270 --> 00:16:17,390
this will be a capital offense.

275
00:16:17,390 --> 00:16:20,150
They deserve it.

276
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:23,720
I won't go back on my promise to you.

277
00:16:24,270 --> 00:16:26,800
I've already requested
Prince Qi's approval

278
00:16:27,030 --> 00:16:28,830
to reopen the Lantai gathering.

279
00:16:29,030 --> 00:16:29,790
Get up first.

280
00:16:30,450 --> 00:16:31,020
Come on.

281
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:35,870
Zhaolin,

282
00:16:37,150 --> 00:16:38,410
when the time comes...

283
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:42,550
you'll be a student of mine,

284
00:16:42,790 --> 00:16:44,240
and no one will ever

285
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:46,600
look down on your background again.

286
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:53,150
Thank you,

287
00:16:54,910 --> 00:16:55,840
Grand Tutor Xie.

288
00:17:02,720 --> 00:17:04,069
Are those people

289
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:06,510
helping you cook the books

290
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,400
actually trustworthy?

291
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:09,200
They don't know

292
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:10,329
what they're doing,

293
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:12,750
nor do they know who they're working for.

294
00:17:12,750 --> 00:17:13,510
Excellent.

295
00:17:42,270 --> 00:17:43,200
Are you alright?

296
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:48,690
Let's go!

297
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:55,100
Hurry.

298
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:04,110
Mr. Liu,

299
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:08,020
since when did you become
Grand Tutor Xie's lackey?

300
00:18:10,480 --> 00:18:12,260
You knew I collected rare books.

301
00:18:12,260 --> 00:18:14,060
Xiao Yao, Xiao Wuyi,

302
00:18:14,510 --> 00:18:17,790
and even Prince Jing'an had
all borrowed and annotated them.

303
00:18:17,790 --> 00:18:20,070
So you used me to obtain

304
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:22,240
the handwriting of every member

305
00:18:22,310 --> 00:18:24,840
of the Xiao family
by borrowing books from me.

306
00:18:25,770 --> 00:18:28,860
Back then, when you gave me
a deed of debt...

307
00:18:29,340 --> 00:18:30,670
I offer this deed of debt

308
00:18:31,030 --> 00:18:31,920
as proof

309
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:34,230
that I'll surely repay the debt someday.

310
00:18:34,230 --> 00:18:36,150
When you said
you'd repay me for saving your life,

311
00:18:36,150 --> 00:18:37,750
you'd already thought of
how you could use me?

312
00:18:37,750 --> 00:18:39,510
Absolutely not! I...

313
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:43,790
I admire you.

314
00:18:46,110 --> 00:18:47,710
But I didn't dare to tell you.

315
00:18:51,830 --> 00:18:52,920
I knew all along.

316
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:57,900
I've frequented the bookstore
these past couple of years.

317
00:18:59,240 --> 00:19:00,780
Could you really not tell
how I felt about you?

318
00:19:00,780 --> 00:19:02,440
It's precisely because I know

319
00:19:02,670 --> 00:19:05,200
that I'm even more aware
I'm not worthy of you.

320
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:06,750
Whether you were the Consort of the Heir
of Prince Jing'an back then

321
00:19:06,750 --> 00:19:07,960
or are the head of the He family now,

322
00:19:07,960 --> 00:19:09,360
I was never worthy of you.

323
00:19:11,550 --> 00:19:12,720
I'm merely a commoner,

324
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:13,880
full of ideals.

325
00:19:14,240 --> 00:19:15,640
Anyone can trample on me.

326
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:17,400
Only Grand Tutor Xie.

327
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:19,060
He promised me.

328
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:20,800
As long as Xiao Wuyi falls

329
00:19:20,960 --> 00:19:23,590
and the noble clans
revive the Lantai gathering,

330
00:19:23,590 --> 00:19:25,320
he'll give me an official post.

331
00:19:36,850 --> 00:19:38,980
You're the third child in your family.

332
00:19:39,310 --> 00:19:41,240
You once studied at Luming Academy

333
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:44,700
and were classmates
with my second brother.

334
00:19:45,270 --> 00:19:46,310
Back then,

335
00:19:46,900 --> 00:19:49,350
I often secretly put on
my second brother's clothes

336
00:19:49,350 --> 00:19:52,150
and sneaked into the academy
to sit in on lectures.

337
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:54,170
We got to know each other over time.

338
00:19:54,690 --> 00:19:56,290
We shared the same interests

339
00:19:56,510 --> 00:19:58,110
and often studied together.

340
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:00,880
It was only then that my brother told you

341
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:02,120
I was actually a girl.

342
00:20:02,930 --> 00:20:04,660
You were shocked yet delighted

343
00:20:05,030 --> 00:20:08,310
and said you'd return home and ask
your parents to arrange our marriage.

344
00:20:08,310 --> 00:20:09,720
But just at that time,

345
00:20:10,270 --> 00:20:11,870
my aunt, Empress Dowager He,

346
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:13,440
was choosing someone from the clan

347
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:15,120
to marry into Prince Jing'an's household.

348
00:20:15,120 --> 00:20:16,520
But I was in love with you.

349
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:18,210
After my aunt found out,

350
00:20:18,310 --> 00:20:19,840
she sent people to kill you.

351
00:20:25,830 --> 00:20:26,790
I thought

352
00:20:27,750 --> 00:20:28,880
you were dead.

353
00:20:31,030 --> 00:20:32,160
But I never imagined

354
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:36,080
that day at the bookstore...

355
00:20:36,350 --> 00:20:37,350
Pei Runheng?

356
00:20:40,030 --> 00:20:41,680
I'd see you again.

357
00:20:43,830 --> 00:20:44,640
Impossible.

358
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:48,400
You definitely got the wrong person.

359
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:50,460
You were born in the Year of the Tiger.

360
00:20:51,550 --> 00:20:54,830
There's a plum blossom-shaped scar
on your left arm.

361
00:20:56,750 --> 00:21:00,200
You got it when you were protecting me
from wild bees while we were

362
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:03,330
picking mulberries in the back mountain
of the academy.

363
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,660
And your handwriting.

364
00:21:08,270 --> 00:21:09,670
I would never mistake it.

365
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:14,920
Then why didn't you tell me sooner?

366
00:21:18,110 --> 00:21:21,030
In the second year after I married into
Prince Jing'an's household,

367
00:21:21,030 --> 00:21:23,240
Empress Dowager He found a pretext

368
00:21:23,440 --> 00:21:24,970
and convicted your family.

369
00:21:25,750 --> 00:21:27,480
Your father and brothers died,

370
00:21:27,590 --> 00:21:30,070
and your mother, in her despair,
took her own life along with your sister.

371
00:21:30,070 --> 00:21:31,800
I'm a daughter of the He family.

372
00:21:32,030 --> 00:21:34,760
Our families have long been
bound by a blood feud.

373
00:21:34,880 --> 00:21:37,080
I didn't dare let you remember the past.

374
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:39,380
I foolishly convinced myself

375
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:42,410
that as long as I didn't speak of it,

376
00:21:42,510 --> 00:21:45,720
we could have a fresh start together.

377
00:21:46,550 --> 00:21:47,880
But I never expected...

378
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:50,270
I never expected

379
00:21:50,270 --> 00:21:52,600
you to be deceived
and used by Xie Huaigui.

380
00:21:53,440 --> 00:21:57,480
Runheng, you can still turn back now.

381
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:02,970
My right hand is ruined.

382
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:05,070
I can no longer prove

383
00:22:05,070 --> 00:22:07,680
that those letters and ledgers
were forged by me.

384
00:22:07,680 --> 00:22:09,070
You are living proof.

385
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:12,000
Jiayu.

386
00:22:23,750 --> 00:22:27,880
What exactly is the crime Grand Tutor Xie
intends to pin on the Xiao family?

387
00:22:28,010 --> 00:22:28,860
Treason...

388
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:35,850
and collaboration with the enemy.

389
00:22:44,270 --> 00:22:46,720
Tell us everything you know.

390
00:22:48,680 --> 00:22:49,680
At this point,

391
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:50,960
Runheng,

392
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:53,600
for the sake of the person you once were,

393
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:55,440
don't keep going down this road.

394
00:23:07,270 --> 00:23:08,800
Third Alley, Shanghe Ward.

395
00:23:09,830 --> 00:23:11,680
The scholars who forged
the letters and ledgers

396
00:23:11,680 --> 00:23:12,880
are all hidden there.

397
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:14,240
If you move quickly,

398
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:16,640
you might still be able to
save some of them.

399
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:21,790
Too late again.

400
00:23:37,030 --> 00:23:38,760
The outcome is not yet decided.

401
00:23:40,350 --> 00:23:42,480
Prince Qi, don't you think
you've come a little early?

402
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:43,610
These past few days,

403
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,760
the evidence has been piling up—

404
00:23:45,830 --> 00:23:47,790
Xiao Yao's corruption
in the grain canal project,

405
00:23:47,790 --> 00:23:50,350
and Xiao Ju's sale of military supplies
and leaking of military intelligence.

406
00:23:50,350 --> 00:23:51,640
Not just your family—

407
00:23:51,750 --> 00:23:54,300
many of the common-born officials
you promoted

408
00:23:54,300 --> 00:23:55,960
have been dragged down with you as well.

409
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:59,310
Now, the public in and out of Jiankang
is outraged,

410
00:24:00,030 --> 00:24:03,350
demanding severe punishment
for your family

411
00:24:03,480 --> 00:24:06,070
and a strict investigation
of common-born officials.

412
00:24:06,070 --> 00:24:09,000
Do you think you still have a way out,

413
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:12,640
Crown Prince Wenxi?

414
00:24:21,070 --> 00:24:24,310
From the day His Majesty returned
the Phoenix Heart Token to you,

415
00:24:24,310 --> 00:24:26,040
I was certain of your identity.

416
00:24:26,880 --> 00:24:28,740
From supervising the grain canal

417
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:32,000
to charges of treason, it's exactly

418
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:36,650
the same pattern as the downfall
of the An and Lu families back then.

419
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:41,370
Grand Tutor Xie has certainly
put a great deal of thought

420
00:24:43,110 --> 00:24:45,370
into choosing the Xiao family's crimes.

421
00:24:47,880 --> 00:24:50,810
So you really do know
the truth behind the An-Lu case.

422
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:52,110
And since you know,

423
00:24:52,440 --> 00:24:53,440
you should also realize

424
00:24:53,440 --> 00:24:55,920
that Grand Tutor Xie isn't
leaving you any way out.

425
00:24:55,920 --> 00:24:57,270
Xie Jiayu acted fast

426
00:24:57,680 --> 00:25:00,550
and found the one
who forged the letters and ledgers.

427
00:25:00,550 --> 00:25:02,070
But that man's hand is ruined.

428
00:25:02,070 --> 00:25:03,070
He can't testify.

429
00:25:05,350 --> 00:25:07,680
For the sake of our past brotherhood,

430
00:25:08,750 --> 00:25:10,400
I can spare your whole family...

431
00:25:10,400 --> 00:25:13,530
I won't agree to the conditions
you're about to propose.

432
00:25:17,550 --> 00:25:19,790
Hand over the Beifu Army
and the Phoenix Heart Token,

433
00:25:19,790 --> 00:25:21,520
and write a divorce agreement.

434
00:25:21,920 --> 00:25:23,960
I want you to tell Xie Jiayu yourself

435
00:25:23,960 --> 00:25:25,560
that you want to divorce her.

436
00:25:27,550 --> 00:25:29,750
Do you honestly think that's possible?

437
00:25:46,240 --> 00:25:47,440
I think it is.

438
00:25:55,980 --> 00:25:58,250
Xie Jiayu is her own person.

439
00:25:58,830 --> 00:25:59,960
Her life

440
00:26:01,030 --> 00:26:02,200
and her feelings

441
00:26:03,310 --> 00:26:05,110
should be hers to choose.

442
00:26:06,480 --> 00:26:08,440
You're forcing her to come back to you—

443
00:26:08,440 --> 00:26:10,070
is it because you love her

444
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:14,160
or because you hate me?

445
00:26:14,180 --> 00:26:17,040
That was Xie Jiayu's own wrong choice
to begin with.

446
00:26:18,270 --> 00:26:19,240
I'm merely giving her

447
00:26:19,240 --> 00:26:20,920
a chance to choose again.

448
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:28,070
Li Yizhi.

449
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:33,840
You shouldn't have dragged the Xiao family

450
00:26:34,070 --> 00:26:36,730
and all those common-born officials
into this.

451
00:26:39,310 --> 00:26:41,920
Do you really think
all those commoners you promoted

452
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:44,450
are people of
both talent and good character?

453
00:26:46,550 --> 00:26:49,400
Cruel and corrupt officials
mostly come from humble origins.

454
00:26:49,400 --> 00:26:52,250
The common people have long since grown
to despise the reforms.

455
00:26:52,250 --> 00:26:55,510
Even if everything you've done
was meant to save the realm,

456
00:26:55,890 --> 00:26:56,810
then tell me—

457
00:26:57,310 --> 00:27:00,750
how many people can
truly understand your intentions?

458
00:27:01,510 --> 00:27:04,040
And how many
would actually appreciate them?

459
00:27:04,680 --> 00:27:06,880
All you'll get is more and more people

460
00:27:07,880 --> 00:27:09,830
wanting you dead.

461
00:27:18,830 --> 00:27:20,110
And you don't fully know

462
00:27:20,110 --> 00:27:21,700
this father of yours either.

463
00:27:21,700 --> 00:27:23,560
Xiao Ju was not dragged into this.

464
00:27:24,310 --> 00:27:25,790
He and your birth mother

465
00:27:26,230 --> 00:27:29,090
were both perpetrators
of the An-Lu wrongful case.

466
00:27:29,920 --> 00:27:31,350
He's selfish and cowardly

467
00:27:31,350 --> 00:27:34,750
and will abandon all moral principles
for his own interests.

468
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:37,410
The downfall of the Xiao family

469
00:27:37,480 --> 00:27:38,480
is inevitable.

470
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:41,360
If you really want to protect Xie Jiayu,

471
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:46,070
divorce is the only path left.

472
00:28:06,510 --> 00:28:08,920
The grain canal collapsed,
the Xiao family embezzled,

473
00:28:08,920 --> 00:28:13,050
Xiao Wuyi was imprisoned, and the ruler
and his subject became estranged.

474
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:14,740
You're very smart.

475
00:28:15,310 --> 00:28:17,350
You know that the truth of the An-Lu case

476
00:28:17,350 --> 00:28:19,150
is Xie Huaigui's real obsession

477
00:28:19,550 --> 00:28:20,750
and that if he learns

478
00:28:21,070 --> 00:28:23,000
Xiao Ju knew of the injustice back then

479
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:24,070
yet concealed it,

480
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:26,680
he will never let the Xiao family go.

481
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:33,410
Xiao Wuyi has been imprisoned.

482
00:28:33,830 --> 00:28:34,790
Are you happy?

483
00:28:39,160 --> 00:28:40,270
If he dies,

484
00:28:40,590 --> 00:28:42,550
Xie Jiayu will be left
without anyone to rely on.

485
00:28:42,550 --> 00:28:45,280
Your brother is now the Regent
in name and in fact.

486
00:28:45,510 --> 00:28:47,440
You can also return to Southern Ye.

487
00:28:57,960 --> 00:28:58,960
I belong

488
00:28:59,790 --> 00:29:01,250
to you now, Your Highness.

489
00:29:02,070 --> 00:29:04,510
And I'll never go back in this life.

490
00:29:05,090 --> 00:29:06,950
Without Xiao Wuyi, the Beifu Army

491
00:29:07,110 --> 00:29:08,770
has lost its fighting spirit.

492
00:29:09,350 --> 00:29:12,830
It'll never again be a match
for Your Highness's Black Eagle Army.

493
00:29:12,830 --> 00:29:14,960
From now on, the border will be secure.

494
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:18,480
I should congratulate Your Highness.

495
00:29:19,750 --> 00:29:20,590
Is that so?

496
00:29:21,550 --> 00:29:24,640
You're helping your brother
eliminate his greatest rival,

497
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:27,300
and yet you still find
such a pretty way to put it.

498
00:29:29,310 --> 00:29:30,170
Your Highness,

499
00:29:30,480 --> 00:29:32,110
all the warriors participating in
today's mounted archery contest

500
00:29:32,110 --> 00:29:32,910
have arrived.

501
00:29:33,270 --> 00:29:35,440
The cattle, sheep, and Ye slaves
have also been brought into the arena.

502
00:29:35,440 --> 00:29:36,200
I know.

503
00:29:38,070 --> 00:29:40,200
Then let me help Your Highness change.

504
00:29:48,590 --> 00:29:49,200
Lejun.

505
00:29:57,480 --> 00:29:58,280
What's wrong?

506
00:29:58,790 --> 00:29:59,830
My child...

507
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:01,710
Our child?

508
00:30:03,300 --> 00:30:04,630
You did this on purpose.

509
00:30:04,840 --> 00:30:05,970
You didn't want him.

510
00:30:06,400 --> 00:30:08,330
You didn't want our child, did you?

511
00:30:09,680 --> 00:30:10,270
I...

512
00:30:11,510 --> 00:30:12,590
didn't...

513
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:19,610
Lejun. Lejun!

514
00:30:25,510 --> 00:30:27,030
We were still a step too late.

515
00:30:27,030 --> 00:30:28,920
We only have Liu Zhaolin as a witness,

516
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:30,360
but his hand is ruined.

517
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:32,510
I'm afraid his testimony alone
won't convince anyone.

518
00:30:32,510 --> 00:30:33,240
Not too late.

519
00:30:33,320 --> 00:30:35,320
At least now we know who's behind it.

520
00:30:35,350 --> 00:30:36,000
Jiayu.

521
00:30:38,270 --> 00:30:39,330
There is something

522
00:30:39,830 --> 00:30:40,960
you need to know now.

523
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:46,030
If Xiao Wuyi
keeps pushing himself like this,

524
00:30:46,030 --> 00:30:47,560
he probably won't even last

525
00:30:48,240 --> 00:30:49,170
another year.

526
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:55,420
Xiao Wuyi didn't mean to keep it from you.

527
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:05,510
Then how is he

528
00:31:06,510 --> 00:31:07,240
now?

529
00:31:09,040 --> 00:31:10,300
It's well controlled.

530
00:31:10,520 --> 00:31:12,850
In enclosed spaces
or in the dark at night,

531
00:31:12,880 --> 00:31:13,720
it worsens.

532
00:31:14,380 --> 00:31:16,180
But he's learned to live with it.

533
00:31:17,770 --> 00:31:19,140
What worries me most now

534
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:22,200
is that the Court of Judicial Review
will use torture.

535
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:23,550
I heard from Yuanji

536
00:31:23,570 --> 00:31:25,310
that Commandant of Justice Lu
is a harsh official.

537
00:31:25,310 --> 00:31:27,370
If Xiao Wuyi's condition worsens...

538
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:30,030
there's no telling what will happen.

539
00:31:30,030 --> 00:31:32,430
For now, the priority is finding a way
to get him out

540
00:31:32,430 --> 00:31:33,560
as soon as possible.

541
00:31:35,970 --> 00:31:38,820
[Grand Tutor's Mansion]

542
00:31:38,870 --> 00:31:40,930
[Xie]

543
00:31:42,350 --> 00:31:44,220
Third Alley, Shanghe Ward
has been emptied.

544
00:31:44,220 --> 00:31:46,750
Grand Tutor Xie,
you've fabricated charges.

545
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:49,480
You framed the Beifu Army commander
who bled

546
00:31:49,480 --> 00:31:51,880
for this nation as a traitor
who colluded with the enemy.

547
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:53,680
When you wake in the middle of the night,

548
00:31:53,680 --> 00:31:56,080
doesn't your conscience ever trouble you?

549
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:01,560
Yaoyao, you're thoughtful.

550
00:32:04,170 --> 00:32:05,610
A troubled conscience?

551
00:32:09,460 --> 00:32:12,060
I'm only doing to him
what he once did to others.

552
00:32:16,680 --> 00:32:17,480
You mean...

553
00:32:18,790 --> 00:32:20,680
Prince Jing'an framed
the An and Lu families?

554
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:22,790
He knew there was an injustice
in the An-Lu case,

555
00:32:22,790 --> 00:32:23,920
yet he concealed it.

556
00:32:24,070 --> 00:32:26,270
How is that any different from framing?

557
00:32:26,350 --> 00:32:27,480
And Xiao Wuyi.

558
00:32:28,510 --> 00:32:30,240
Since he is Crown Prince Wenxi,

559
00:32:30,350 --> 00:32:31,640
he naturally must atone for

560
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:33,900
the sins committed by his birth parents.

561
00:32:42,000 --> 00:32:44,750
Yaoyao, concocting an unjust case

562
00:32:45,350 --> 00:32:48,110
might be unfair to others,

563
00:32:48,400 --> 00:32:49,710
but to the Xiao family

564
00:32:49,880 --> 00:32:51,590
and Crown Prince Wenxi,

565
00:32:52,830 --> 00:32:54,110
it's Heaven's will.

566
00:32:55,030 --> 00:32:57,550
Heaven's justice always comes full circle—

567
00:32:58,070 --> 00:32:59,270
this is retribution.

568
00:33:02,880 --> 00:33:03,510
Father.

569
00:33:05,680 --> 00:33:06,880
What really happened

570
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:09,410
to the An and Lu families back then?

571
00:33:13,310 --> 00:33:17,110
Just as the Xiao family is
experiencing today.

572
00:33:17,280 --> 00:33:20,090
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

573
00:33:20,830 --> 00:33:21,590
My Lady, how did you know

574
00:33:21,590 --> 00:33:24,250
about the mechanism
in Grand Tutor Xie's study?

575
00:33:25,070 --> 00:33:26,110
I was mischievous as a child

576
00:33:26,110 --> 00:33:28,370
and stumbled upon
the mechanism by accident.

577
00:33:28,370 --> 00:33:30,570
You know what's inside the box, My Lady?

578
00:33:31,590 --> 00:33:32,270
No.

579
00:33:32,440 --> 00:33:35,570
But they must be extremely important
to Grand Tutor Xie.

580
00:33:35,920 --> 00:33:37,960
Qizhou, Qingzhou...

581
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:39,350
And Luzhou.

582
00:33:41,550 --> 00:33:42,480
Where did you go?

583
00:33:42,830 --> 00:33:44,070
After His Highness was imprisoned,

584
00:33:44,070 --> 00:33:46,120
Qing Long and I were ordered to
go to Luzhou to find someone.

585
00:33:46,120 --> 00:33:46,680
Who?

586
00:33:46,960 --> 00:33:50,070
Prince Qi's adoptive mother,
Madam Wang of the Lu family.

587
00:33:50,070 --> 00:33:52,270
Originally, she'd always been
under His Highness's control,

588
00:33:52,270 --> 00:33:53,920
but she was poisoned at some point.

589
00:33:53,920 --> 00:33:55,070
We were still a step too late.

590
00:33:55,070 --> 00:33:56,270
A step too late again.

591
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:58,000
Actually, Her Highness Princess Yunzhao

592
00:33:58,000 --> 00:33:59,860
also sent me to these three places

593
00:33:59,880 --> 00:34:01,510
to look for Madam Wang of the Lu family.

594
00:34:01,510 --> 00:34:03,920
It was shortly after
Prince Qi was appointed Regent.

595
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:04,880
That's also why

596
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:07,760
I didn't go to Lingfeng Fort
with Her Highness.

597
00:34:09,560 --> 00:34:11,219
What did Mother send you to do?

598
00:34:11,850 --> 00:34:14,250
To investigate Prince Qi's true identity.

599
00:34:14,510 --> 00:34:16,510
For Mao, for our family,

600
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:19,679
you must be this pawn.

601
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:22,280
I finally understand

602
00:34:23,440 --> 00:34:24,969
why Lejun killed my mother,

603
00:34:25,630 --> 00:34:26,840
why my father and mother

604
00:34:26,840 --> 00:34:28,500
divorced after I got married,

605
00:34:29,840 --> 00:34:31,030
and why my mother never approved

606
00:34:31,030 --> 00:34:32,630
of Mao and me being together.

607
00:34:36,190 --> 00:34:37,520
I understand it all now.

608
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:43,210
[Shezhang Hall]

609
00:34:49,070 --> 00:34:51,280
I, Xie Jiayu,
Consort of the Heir of Prince Jing'an,

610
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:53,139
pay respects to Regent Prince Qi.

611
00:34:59,670 --> 00:35:00,670
Let her in.

612
00:35:11,150 --> 00:35:12,960
The corruption and treason of

613
00:35:13,280 --> 00:35:16,080
Prince Jing'an's family
have all been confirmed.

614
00:35:18,280 --> 00:35:20,360
No matter how badly you want to save him,

615
00:35:20,360 --> 00:35:22,670
Xiao Wuyi has no other choice

616
00:35:23,230 --> 00:35:25,690
but to hand over
the command of the Beifu Army

617
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:27,150
and write a confession.

618
00:35:27,230 --> 00:35:28,000
I came today

619
00:35:28,480 --> 00:35:29,740
to give you something.

620
00:35:35,830 --> 00:35:37,510
[Li Mao's Lineage Investigation]

621
00:35:50,840 --> 00:35:52,800
Xiao Wuyi has known
your true identity all along.

622
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:54,330
If he wanted your position,

623
00:35:54,760 --> 00:35:56,420
it would've been his long ago.

624
00:35:58,070 --> 00:35:59,400
You trust him that much?

625
00:36:00,230 --> 00:36:02,030
The facts speak for themselves,

626
00:36:02,110 --> 00:36:03,910
whether you believe them or not.

627
00:36:08,250 --> 00:36:10,000
And if I keep you here,

628
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:12,620
then all this evidence

629
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:15,650
will mean nothing.

630
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,730
Yaoyao, don't force me.

631
00:36:21,450 --> 00:36:23,300
I'm not the Li Mao I used to be.

632
00:36:24,090 --> 00:36:25,840
If I can't get what I want,

633
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:27,640
then we'll all go down together.

634
00:36:30,320 --> 00:36:31,980
I'll give you one last chance.

635
00:36:33,230 --> 00:36:35,230
Take off those robes
of the Heir's Consort,

636
00:36:35,230 --> 00:36:36,230
leave Xiao Wuyi,

637
00:36:36,570 --> 00:36:38,100
and stay by my side forever.

638
00:36:39,390 --> 00:36:40,150
Okay?

639
00:36:48,430 --> 00:36:49,110
No.

640
00:36:50,110 --> 00:36:53,280
I also have the letters
exchanged between Grand Tutor Xie

641
00:36:53,280 --> 00:36:55,340
and your wet nurse
over the past dozen years.

642
00:36:55,340 --> 00:36:56,780
He still doesn't know

643
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:58,610
that I took the letters.

644
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:00,720
I'll give you three days.

645
00:37:01,000 --> 00:37:02,200
If, after three days,

646
00:37:02,330 --> 00:37:04,400
Wuyi and the rest of the Xiao family
have not returned

647
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:07,180
and if the Court of Judicial Review
has not cleared their name,

648
00:37:07,180 --> 00:37:09,380
then this record of your true identity,

649
00:37:10,320 --> 00:37:11,960
along with the letters
between the Grand Tutor

650
00:37:11,960 --> 00:37:14,000
and your wet nurse
over the past dozen years,

651
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:16,060
will be spread throughout Jiankang.

652
00:37:22,590 --> 00:37:23,360
Mao,

653
00:37:24,630 --> 00:37:26,710
whether I'm the Heir's Consort or not,

654
00:37:26,710 --> 00:37:27,910
I'm still Xie Jiayu.

655
00:37:28,480 --> 00:37:30,340
Whether I'm with Xiao Wuyi or not,

656
00:37:31,070 --> 00:37:33,470
I won't choose to
enter the palace with you.

657
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:37,230
These past few years,
I've traveled to many places

658
00:37:37,230 --> 00:37:38,560
and lived very happily.

659
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:41,500
Don't stay trapped in the past

660
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:43,820
and let it become your obsession.

661
00:37:45,650 --> 00:37:47,580
You were never this kind of person.

662
00:38:05,110 --> 00:38:08,550
[Court of Judicial Review]

663
00:38:29,510 --> 00:38:30,550
Yaoyao came.

664
00:38:34,150 --> 00:38:35,510
When did you

665
00:38:36,260 --> 00:38:38,260
start suspecting my true identity?

666
00:38:40,150 --> 00:38:43,670
From the moment Prince Changsha
mutinied to force the abdication

667
00:38:43,670 --> 00:38:46,680
and you were suddenly pushed to
the position of Regent.

668
00:38:46,680 --> 00:38:47,470
I thought

669
00:38:48,320 --> 00:38:51,380
it was at least
after Lejun got rid of Princess Yunzhao.

670
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:53,900
I didn't expect it to be even earlier.

671
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:55,670
That night,

672
00:38:57,070 --> 00:38:59,030
when I saw you in Jiankang Palace,

673
00:38:59,280 --> 00:39:00,210
I was wondering:

674
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:02,190
Grand Tutor Xie had been plotting
for a long time,

675
00:39:02,190 --> 00:39:04,270
so why did he choose you specifically?

676
00:39:04,270 --> 00:39:05,310
As expected,

677
00:39:06,580 --> 00:39:08,920
His Majesty immediately
sent people to Qizhou

678
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:10,920
to investigate your true identity.

679
00:39:11,710 --> 00:39:14,170
Princess Yunzhao's Shadow Envoys also went

680
00:39:14,550 --> 00:39:17,010
and found out the truth
they shouldn't have.

681
00:39:17,030 --> 00:39:19,320
But at that time, why didn't you...

682
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:20,670
Why didn't I expose you

683
00:39:21,320 --> 00:39:24,250
and make this crime
of deceiving the emperor public?

684
00:39:31,550 --> 00:39:33,810
Because you and I have the same ambition.

685
00:39:35,150 --> 00:39:36,610
What I cannot accomplish,

686
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:39,210
you can accomplish in my place.

687
00:39:40,400 --> 00:39:41,920
I don't need an incompetent good man

688
00:39:41,920 --> 00:39:43,450
standing in that position.

689
00:39:43,880 --> 00:39:45,730
Ambition, ruthless methods—

690
00:39:45,760 --> 00:39:47,690
whoever holds that position needs both.

691
00:39:47,690 --> 00:39:50,820
I don't think
there's anything wrong with your origins.

692
00:39:55,000 --> 00:39:56,800
You don't care about the throne,

693
00:39:57,910 --> 00:39:59,580
but you need a helper.

694
00:40:00,550 --> 00:40:02,230
So you chose me.

695
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:05,630
For your ambition,

696
00:40:05,630 --> 00:40:06,800
I lost Yaoyao.

697
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:08,660
I lost the life I was meant to have!

698
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:13,140
I am not willing to be your puppet,

699
00:40:16,030 --> 00:40:18,670
and even less willing to accept
that Yaoyao remains so devoted to you.

700
00:40:18,670 --> 00:40:20,590
She loves freedom more than anything,

701
00:40:20,590 --> 00:40:22,400
yet she's willing to be bound to your side

702
00:40:22,400 --> 00:40:24,000
and give everything for you!

703
00:40:35,590 --> 00:40:38,920
Those noble clans thought
that making peace with Northern Qin

704
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:41,320
could buy a corner
of peace and prosperity.

705
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:46,130
But that's only a fleeting prosperity
confined within Jiankang's walls.

706
00:40:46,320 --> 00:40:47,360
Beyond the city,

707
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:48,550
countless people on the Northern Border

708
00:40:48,550 --> 00:40:50,000
still live amid war.

709
00:40:54,360 --> 00:40:55,550
If we don't eliminate Northern Qin

710
00:40:55,550 --> 00:40:56,440
and reclaim our lost homeland,

711
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:58,100
there can never be true peace!

712
00:40:58,630 --> 00:40:59,280
Yizhi,

713
00:41:00,100 --> 00:41:01,550
these were your own words

714
00:41:01,550 --> 00:41:03,150
while you were fleeing here.

715
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:05,550
It was you who forgot.

716
00:41:16,630 --> 00:41:17,960
The person who chose you

717
00:41:19,790 --> 00:41:20,650
was never me...

718
00:41:25,360 --> 00:41:26,760
but yourself.

